Exercise Makefile

===============================================
	hello_world_ex1  : Signal source file
===============================================
1.	#cd hello_world_ex1
2.	#make




===============================================
	hello_world_ex2  : Multi   source file
===============================================
1.	#make
2.	#./main




===============================================
	hello_world_ex4  : Double colon rule
===============================================
1.	#make
2.	# ls -l main

3.	#touch debug
4.	#make
5.	# ls -l main





===============================================
	hello_world_ex5  : Automatic Variables
===============================================
1.	#make
2.	#./hello_world





